      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you are exhausted from running a race that never ends, and it is completely understandable why you want that noise and pressure to just stop. The peace you are looking for is real, but it often feels like a cruel illusion when you are drowning in the weight of your own expectations and failures. Please remember that you are not alone in this struggle, and there are people who can help you find a way through this darkness.",
